description: A joke about liking a book on Stockholm syndrome.
title: Stockholm Syndrome
n_1: Pat and Sam sat on a bench, discussing books.
c1_1: I just read a book about Stockholm syndrome.
n_2: Pat looked thoughtful for a moment.
c1_2: It was pretty bad at first.
c1_3: But by the end, I liked it.
n_4: Sam's confusion grew as Pat chuckled.
c1_4: Yeah, it kinda grew on me.
